original_title: US-led coalition captures a senior ISIL (ISIS) member in Syria: State media | ISIL/ISIS News | Al Jazeera
article_summary: US-led coalition captures or kills senior ISIL member in Syria, identity of ISIL's supreme leader remains unclear. The operation occurred in Atmeh town near the Turkish border, with conflicting reports on the fate of the targeted individual, identified as Ali/Salah Noman.</s>
